metadata.name: STARRY GIRL 2022  - ARICK X STARGIRL by SABET
metadata.description:
This is the first ever collab between Ali Sabet and Arick Cohen Salmea (the artist formerly known as Moriartsy).  Perhaps this is the first of many collabs, or perhaps you're getting a one and only of all time. 

It is my great pleasure to work on this creative piece with such a fantastic creative force as Sabet and I feel truly blessed to have this opportunity.

To me this piece symbolizes the power of endless possibilities.
